{"tid":1487163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前往澳洲旅遊的香港旅客警告！戴口罩坐直升機睇大堡礁可能有機會被槍斃？","createTime":"2019-08-19T06:53:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T09:50:54.000Z","uid":213508,"like":74,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"e307f37496e672c983b52a6d904b32510752984d","tid":1487163,"uid":213508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:53:52.000Z","msg":"主題：前往澳洲旅遊的香港旅客警告！戴口罩坐直升機睇大堡礁可能有機會被槍斃？ <br />\n轉發自內文:<br />\n嘩！連澳洲既直升機公司都話要槍斃香港既&rdquo;口罩黨&ldquo; 我真係登香港遊客好擔心 會唔會搭搭下直升機都會突然墜毀？如果係，保險公司因為乘客戴口罩而唔會有得賠架？<br />\n<br />\n上網搜一搜 呢間皇家直升機公司叫 <span style=\"color: red;\">Nautilus Aviation</span>專門係北部昆士蘭開恩茲睇大堡礁 仲要以紅色空中法拉利自稱。網上仲話呢間皇家同幾間大既游船公司做直升機服務，好似好多大既旅行社都去澳洲都會去大堡礁。 各位巴絲 可唔可以幫手查下香港邊間旅行社會去呢d 船 因為真係幾得人驚lor。因為呢位 Coco 小姐好明顯就係係間直升機公司既員工啦，其實真係會對華人（特別係香港人）戴口罩既構成嚴重人身安全危險。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ovxVDY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ovxVDY.jpg&h=40ad8e8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/koFJ2iZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkoFJ2iZ.jpg&h=0c41d6f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLS8tY0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLS8tY0.jpg&h=b0dfae80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">公司Link</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nautilusaviation.com.au\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nautilusaviation.com.au&d=00b%2B5OzPsUCZ7nX0ilF46%2F7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=e0bcd00b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nautilusaviation.com.au</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又係班蝗國人<br />\n要佢地柒出國際 都要自己小心<br />\n無衛生常識既蝗國人要開槍喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f175b1c1e6c403fb01c52ef71cd15740cad3b6","tid":1487163,"uid":213508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:27:22.000Z","msg":"推一個"},{"pid":"89e2ac9d459218758f9c433d56e78f82fd298a08","tid":1487163,"uid":1417